{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1096,"text":"It was the end of October\nin the mountains in Austria."},{"time":5442,"text":"I was there on a field trip\nwith my architecture students from Zurich."},{"time":9660,"text":"And when we reached a high valley,"},{"time":13799,"text":"I surprised them with the news\nthat there was no hut"},{"time":16292,"text":"or hotel booked for the night."},{"time":19552,"text":"It was not a mistake."},{"time":21243,"text":"It was totally on purpose."},{"time":25093,"text":"The challenge was to build our own shelter\nwith whatever we could find."},{"time":30662,"text":"And we all survived."},{"time":32078,"text":"It was cold, it was really tough ..."},{"time":35022,"text":"and it was a great learning experience"},{"time":37729,"text":"to discover that there are a lot\nof resources given by nature for free,"},{"time":41563,"text":"and all that we need\nis our sensitivity to see them ..."},{"time":46210,"text":"and our creativity to use them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50330,"text":"I found myself in a similar situation."},{"time":54425,"text":"When I was an architecture student\nabout 13 years ago,"},{"time":58950,"text":"I went to Bangladesh\nto a remote village called Rudrapur"},{"time":62263,"text":"with the aim to design and build\na school as my thesis project."},{"time":66188,"text":"I had lived in that village before\nwhen I was 19 and a volunteer"},{"time":69407,"text":"at Dipshikha, a Bangladeshi NGO\nfor rural development."},{"time":72368,"text":"And what I had learned from them"},{"time":74074,"text":"was that the most sustainable strategy\nfor sustainable development"},{"time":78876,"text":"is to cherish and to use\nyour very own resources and potential,"},{"time":84059,"text":"and not get dependent on external factors."},{"time":87512,"text":"And this is what I tried to do\nwith my architecture as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91359,"text":"In terms of suitable building\nmaterials for my school,"},{"time":94764,"text":"I didn't have to look far."},{"time":96718,"text":"They were right under my feet:"},{"time":99732,"text":"mud, earth, dirt, clay,\nhowever you call it ..."},{"time":104788,"text":"and bamboo that was growing all around."},{"time":109400,"text":"Electricity in remote Bangladesh is rare,"},{"time":113559,"text":"but we didn't need it."},{"time":114789,"text":"We had human energy"},{"time":116412,"text":"and the people were happy\nto have the work."},{"time":120188,"text":"Tools were an issue, too,"},{"time":122151,"text":"but we had these guys,"},{"time":123738,"text":"water buffalos."},{"time":126730,"text":"We had also tried a bit cows,"},{"time":128890,"text":"but interestingly,\nthey were too intelligent."},{"time":132010,"text":"They were always stepping\nin the holes of the previous round."},{"time":134930,"text":"They wouldn't mix the mud, the straw --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":136812,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":137886,"text":"the sand, which are\nthe ingredients in the walls."},{"time":142171,"text":"And except a small team of consultants"},{"time":144569,"text":"like my partner\nfor realization, Eike Roswag,"},{"time":146696,"text":"and my basket-weaver cousin, Emmanuel,"},{"time":149338,"text":"it was all built by craftsmen\nfrom the village."},{"time":155613,"text":"And this is the METI school\nafter six months of construction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158921,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":161288,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162471,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164097,"text":"Load-bearing earth walls\nthat really ground the school,"},{"time":168226,"text":"and large bamboo structures\nthat bring the lightness in."},{"time":173635,"text":"That's the classroom on the ground floor."},{"time":177072,"text":"Attached to it are the caves."},{"time":179763,"text":"They're for reading,\nfor snuggling, for solo work,"},{"time":182201,"text":"for meditation, for playing ..."},{"time":184891,"text":"and the classroom on the top."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189831,"text":"The children all signed\nwith their names in Bengali the doors,"},{"time":193638,"text":"and they did not only sign,\nthey also helped building the school."},{"time":198207,"text":"And I'm sure you all had your hands\nin mud or clay before."},{"time":201133,"text":"It's wonderful to touch. I love it."},{"time":202970,"text":"The children loved it."},{"time":204894,"text":"And can you imagine the feeling\nof a small boy or a girl"},{"time":209773,"text":"or an illiterate day laborer standing\nin front of that school building"},{"time":213726,"text":"and knowing that you built this"},{"time":215291,"text":"out of the ordinary bamboo\nand just the dirt underneath your feet,"},{"time":218909,"text":"using nothing but your hands?"},{"time":223561,"text":"That gives such an enormous boost\nof trust and confidence"},{"time":229262,"text":"in yourself and the community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232810,"text":"And in the material."},{"time":235348,"text":"Especially mud has a very poor image."},{"time":238241,"text":"When we think of mud, we think of dirt --"},{"time":241369,"text":"it's ugly, it's nondurable --"},{"time":243607,"text":"and this is the image I want to change."},{"time":247159,"text":"In fact, it's the 11th rainy season\nfor this school now,"},{"time":250930,"text":"really harsh, horizontal monsoon rains,"},{"time":254208,"text":"and the walls are standing strong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":257131,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":261664,"text":"So how does it work?"},{"time":263030,"text":"First rule, a good foundation\nthat keeps the wall dry from the ground,"},{"time":267210,"text":"and second rule, a good roof\nthat protects from the top,"},{"time":270930,"text":"and third rule, erosion control."},{"time":274193,"text":"Mud walls need speed breakers"},{"time":276503,"text":"so that the rainwater\ncannot run down the wall fast,"},{"time":280735,"text":"and these speed breakers\ncould be lines of bamboo"},{"time":284041,"text":"or stones or straw mixed into the mud,"},{"time":287646,"text":"just like a hill needs trees or rocks\nin order to prevent erosion."},{"time":292931,"text":"It works just the same way."},{"time":295340,"text":"And people always ask me\nif I have to add cement to the mud,"},{"time":299397,"text":"and the answer is no."},{"time":301311,"text":"There is no stabilizer,\nno coating on these walls,"},{"time":305074,"text":"only in the foundation."},{"time":308294,"text":"So this is the close-up of the wall"},{"time":310136,"text":"after 10 rainy seasons,"},{"time":313620,"text":"and as much as I grew a bit older,"},{"time":316084,"text":"the wall got some wrinkles as well."},{"time":317830,"text":"The edges my not be as sharp as before,"},{"time":320021,"text":"but it still looks pretty good,"},{"time":322197,"text":"and if it needs repairing,"},{"time":323951,"text":"it is really easy to do."},{"time":325966,"text":"You just take the broken part,"},{"time":327733,"text":"make it wet, and put it back on the wall,"},{"time":330495,"text":"and it will look the same as before."},{"time":332542,"text":"Wish that would work on me, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334109,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":338685,"text":"Yeah, and the great thing is,"},{"time":340865,"text":"if an earth wall is not needed anymore,"},{"time":343310,"text":"it can go back to the ground it came from,"},{"time":346575,"text":"turn into a garden,"},{"time":348507,"text":"or get fully recycled\nwithout any loss of quality."},{"time":352607,"text":"There's no other material\nthat can do this,"},{"time":354722,"text":"and this is why mud is so excellent\nin terms of environmental performance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360421,"text":"What about the economic sustainability?"},{"time":363252,"text":"When we built the school,"},{"time":364542,"text":"I practically lived\non the construction site,"},{"time":366943,"text":"and in the evening, I used to go\nwith the workers to the market,"},{"time":369991,"text":"and I could see\nhow they spent their money."},{"time":372984,"text":"And they would buy\nthe vegetables from their neighbors,"},{"time":376308,"text":"they would get a new haircut\nor a new blouse from the tailor."},{"time":380858,"text":"And because the main part\nof the building budget"},{"time":384740,"text":"was spent on craftsmanship,"},{"time":386909,"text":"the school wasn't just a building,"},{"time":389365,"text":"it became a real catalyst\nfor local development,"},{"time":393553,"text":"and that made me happy."},{"time":396989,"text":"If I had designed the school\nin cement and steel,"},{"time":399411,"text":"this money would have been exported\nand lost for those families."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404514,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":409935,"text":"The building budget at that time\nwas 35,000 euros --"},{"time":413530,"text":"it's probably doubled by now --"},{"time":415515,"text":"and this is a lot of money\nfor that region,"},{"time":418627,"text":"and especially because this money\nis working within the community"},{"time":422656,"text":"and rotating fast,"},{"time":423958,"text":"and not on the stock market."},{"time":426402,"text":"So when it comes to the economic\nsustainability of my project,"},{"time":431283,"text":"my main question is, who gets the profit?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":436949,"text":"How many of you in here"},{"time":438990,"text":"have some experience\nliving in a mud house?"},{"time":441514,"text":"Chris Anderson, where is your hand?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":443575,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":444656,"text":"You? OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447139,"text":"Yeah."},{"time":448314,"text":"It seems totally out of our focus,"},{"time":451503,"text":"but approximately three billion people\nall around the planet"},{"time":456161,"text":"are living in earth houses,"},{"time":458668,"text":"and it is a traditional building material"},{"time":460978,"text":"in Europe just as much as in Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466076,"text":"Strangely enough,"},{"time":467641,"text":"mud is not considered worthy\nof being studied at universities ..."},{"time":472281,"text":"so I brought the dirt to Harvard,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":475503,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":477734,"text":"precisely 60 tons of dirt\nright in front of the main facade"},{"time":481734,"text":"of the Graduate School of Design."},{"time":485478,"text":"Students and faculty\nrolled up their sleeves,"},{"time":487646,"text":"got their hands dirty"},{"time":488825,"text":"and transformed the front\ninto a warm place for people to gather."},{"time":493248,"text":"Children would climb the structures,"},{"time":494988,"text":"skaters would ride the ramp,"},{"time":496529,"text":"students having lunch breaks,"},{"time":498299,"text":"and it was particularly fascinating to see\nhow many people were touching the wall,"},{"time":502395,"text":"and we usually don't go around cities\ncaressing our facades, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":506272,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":512366,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":516603,"text":"Of course, this was a small-scale project,"},{"time":518634,"text":"but in terms of awareness-building\nand in terms of education,"},{"time":521754,"text":"it was like an acupuncture trigger point."},{"time":525701,"text":"And in fact, in more and more countries,"},{"time":529305,"text":"load-bearing earthen structures\nare not allowed to be built anymore"},{"time":534314,"text":"although they're traditional\nand have lasted for hundreds of years,"},{"time":537840,"text":"and not because the material is weak,"},{"time":539880,"text":"but because there are\nno architects and engineers"},{"time":543056,"text":"who know how to deal with that material."},{"time":545516,"text":"So education on all levels,"},{"time":547214,"text":"for craftsmen, engineers and architects,"},{"time":549914,"text":"is really strongly needed."},{"time":552085,"text":"Equally important\nis technological development,"},{"time":555453,"text":"like prefabrication developed\nby my colleague Martin Rauch,"},{"time":558570,"text":"who is an Austrian artist\nand expert in earthen structures."},{"time":562580,"text":"And he has created technologies\nfor rammed earth elements,"},{"time":566214,"text":"for prefabrication\nof rammed earth elements"},{"time":568671,"text":"that include insulation,\nwall heatings and coolings"},{"time":572456,"text":"and all sorts of electrical fittings"},{"time":574281,"text":"that can be layered\nto multistoried buildings,"},{"time":576598,"text":"and this is important in order to scale up"},{"time":579299,"text":"and in order to [speed] up the processes,"},{"time":581291,"text":"like in the Ricola Herb Center\nin Switzerland."}]},{"cues":[{"time":586555,"text":"And finally, we need good built projects"},{"time":589707,"text":"that prove you can build\nwith an ancient material"},{"time":592826,"text":"in a very modern way."},{"time":595434,"text":"It is not a matter\nof how old a material is;"},{"time":599152,"text":"it's a matter of our creative\nability to use it today."},{"time":604936,"text":"These, for example, are three hostels"},{"time":607215,"text":"that I did in China in the village Baoxi,"},{"time":609586,"text":"about six hours by bus from Shanghai."},{"time":613859,"text":"The outside shape is woven bamboo,"},{"time":616574,"text":"and the inside core\nis stones and rammed earth."},{"time":621058,"text":"And it is a traditional building material."},{"time":623538,"text":"Even large parts\nof the Great Wall of China"},{"time":625755,"text":"have been built with rammed earth,"},{"time":627424,"text":"but it's getting replaced by concrete."}]},{"cues":[{"time":630411,"text":"And this trend is happening very fast."},{"time":633909,"text":"Within only a couple of years,"},{"time":636909,"text":"China has consumed more cement\nthan the United States"},{"time":639926,"text":"in the entire 20th century."},{"time":642618,"text":"And this trend of replacing\nnatural building materials"},{"time":646151,"text":"with materials that require\na lot of energy,"},{"time":648428,"text":"that are energy-intensive,"},{"time":650238,"text":"and that emit CO2"},{"time":652303,"text":"is really clearly contributing\nto climate change."},{"time":655667,"text":"And we have alternatives,"},{"time":657104,"text":"such as mud, stones, timber,\nbamboo, earth,"},{"time":661379,"text":"that are totally effective options\nfor all sorts of purposes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665926,"text":"This, for example,\nis an office building that we did"},{"time":668497,"text":"for Omicron Electronics in Austria."},{"time":670902,"text":"Mud is healthy for the planet,\nbut also for the human bodies,"},{"time":673823,"text":"and the material is low-tech,"},{"time":676489,"text":"but the performance is high-tech."},{"time":678736,"text":"The earth walls keep the highly\nsophisticated tools in the building safe"},{"time":682839,"text":"by naturally regulating moisture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":685590,"text":"And this wall in my own home"},{"time":689126,"text":"is our humidfier."},{"time":692372,"text":"We love our six tons of dirt at home"},{"time":695326,"text":"not only because\nit's healthy and sustainable."},{"time":698397,"text":"Its archaic warmth\nis touching deep within."}]},{"cues":[{"time":702708,"text":"My personal dream is to build\na mud skyscraper right in Manhattan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":707820,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":709883,"text":"Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711058,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":713281,"text":"And this dream isn't so crazy"},{"time":714854,"text":"if you think of the mud city\nof Shibam in Yemen"},{"time":717070,"text":"that was built in the 16th century"},{"time":718959,"text":"and has lasted now for 500 years."},{"time":723267,"text":"What was possible that long ago\nis possible today as well,"},{"time":727398,"text":"and we can apply\nall our technical know-how"},{"time":731026,"text":"to these ancient materials"},{"time":733060,"text":"so that it meets our needs and our dreams."}]},{"cues":[{"time":738403,"text":"All around us,"},{"time":740301,"text":"and just below our feet ..."},{"time":743060,"text":"are wonderful natural building materials."},{"time":745851,"text":"Let's use them."},{"time":748221,"text":"And I deeply believe"},{"time":750161,"text":"our homes, our work spaces, our cities"},{"time":753716,"text":"would become more healthy and sustainable"},{"time":757540,"text":"and more humane"},{"time":760087,"text":"and beautiful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":761932,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":763107,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}